- LAN port: 32108 (UDP broadcast for discovery)
- One UDP socket, 8 logical channels multiplexed
- DRW pipeline: in-flight window max=64 packets, retransmit after 0.5s
- CyclicU16: 16-bit unsigned wraparound; diff(a,b) with wrap-around; window check: b is 'after' a if diff < 32768
- Xzyh frame: 16-byte header + variable payload, channel 0 and 1
- Aabb frame: file transfer on channel 1, includes CRC
- PacketType is a uint32 enum (0x00000000 etc.) — copy ALL values from Python pppp.py exactly
- Package: github.com/django1982/ankerctl/internal/pppp/protocol and .../client

